dialogue: I feel so refreshed after practising my guitar! What have you done today Jush?
BASEBALL BASEBALL I BATTED 10000000000000 METERS TODAY!
Oh my dear Jush, that is not a good way to spend your time! Come let me show you!
Wait Jush, do you hear that?
EHHH HEAR? EARS? I HAVE EARS!!
MY DEAR JUSH! THOSE ARE MY FANS, THEY ARE COMING FOR ME!!
FRET NOT JUSH, I WILL PROTECT US! WITH THIS GUITAR!
I HEAR TROUBLE, CARA! I think your fans are angry with you!
DON'T WORRY I WILL BEAT THEM UP! HAHAHA!
